metadata.name: Zyggos4Ukraine #1
metadata.description:
Zyggo Distrikt launched a quirky 3333 NFTs collection that stands for MetaHumanity by directing ALL sales profits to organizations that support Ukrainian refugees. Inspired by Ukraine’s culture and by Peace symbolism, these curious Zyggos were generated by using 150+ possible traits (clothing, expressions, accessories, etc.) and will conquer the heart of the Ethereum Blockchain as ERC-721 tokens.
WHY OWN A ZYGGO 
You limit the pain of the war, by helping the victims.
You inspire others to act for peace and solidarity, by showcasing your Zyggo NFT.
You become a Zyggo Coalition Member and unlock early-benefits for our upcoming non-charity NFT collections.
Discover our crypto4Ukraine movement on https://www.zyggodistrikt.com/ and help us make a difference. We can’t do it without you!
